skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: seahawks loss recovery
des:
Seahawks Loss Recovery is a skill to help you recover from a tough Seahawks loss. It was made on the eve of a recent Monday evening, and hopefully it will help some fellow Seahawks fans to get through the tough times we (may) have ahead.

Don't quit on them now!

You can say:

"Alexa, open Seahawks Loss Recovery"
"Alexa, start Seahawks Loss Recovery"
"Alexa, launch Seahawks Loss Recovery"
